sd.PT_NAME: Loss of personal independence in daily activities

freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Feeling faint - like I am about to faint.Feeling too tired, needing to sleep and not able to walk much.
My physical reactions and continuous thinking are way off. I find myself getting extremely tired after just a little activity.

freetext.HEALTHCARE_VISITS_OTHER: I think I'm going to call them in a few minutes
freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I feel totally wiped out in a weird way I actually feel very good but also feel almost dizzy almost faint. It might also be from arrhythmia.

freetext.HEALTHCARE_VISITS_OTHER: Yesterday I called the nurse hotline the nurse wanted me to go into the emergency room because of all the numbness and at that time I told him I left I was closed more than my right I didn't go and most of those symptoms disappeared
freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Yesterday 2 hours after receiving the vaccine the left side of my face especially my lips went numb I think my shoulder as well it lasted till 6 hours later
Left side of face feels puffy.
My skin had like hives the last couple of days that's gone but today I have a cold
The rash felt more like hives. It did respond to Claritin. I forgot to mention on the previous days I had jaw pain and ear pain on the right side oh maybe I did mention it
